182209.title: Caulfield Station: Temporary car park closures from Friday 30 August to Monday 2 September 2019
182209.description: Caulfield Station will be affected by temporary long-term car space closures from 3pm Friday 30 August to 4am Monday 2 September, due to train replacement bus operations..

181613.title: Cranbourne, Frankston and Pakenham lines: Buses replace trains between Parliament and Caulfield from 8.20pm Friday 30 August to last train Sunday 1 September 2019
181613.description: Buses will replace train services between Parliament and Caulfield stations from 8.20pm Friday 30 August to last train Sunday 1 September 2019, while project works take place.

175928.title: Carrum Station: Temporary station closure from 1.15am Saturday 6 July 2019 to early 2020
175928.description: Carrum Station is temporarily closed from 1.15am Saturday 6 July 2019 to early 2020, due to Carrum Level Crossing Removal works.
